With the frequency that a ranger/warrior/paladin's weapons become damaged<br>
they acquire some skill in caring for and repairing them.  Also able to<br>
help the smiths who do the full repairs, the smiths in their kindness,<br>
reduce the cost for repairing the items to full condition.  This is an<br>
autoskill.<br>
